  "body": "As a user\r\nI want my mutual contact requests to be synced across devices\r\nSo that I can communicate with my mutual contacts on each device\r\n\r\n### Description\r\n\r\nWe haven't tested mutual contact requests when two devices are paired, so there's a few cases that we need to check and fix if not working.\r\n\r\nA is a pk, B is a pk, \r\nA1 is a device with pk A\r\nA2 is a different device with pk A\r\n\r\n### Syncing with sync all \r\n\r\n1) A1 creates an account, enables mutual contact requests\r\n2) B1 creates an account, enables mutual contact requests\r\n3) A1 sends a contact request to B1\r\n4) B1 accepts the contact request\r\n5) A2 creates an account\r\n6) A1 & A2 enables pairing\r\n7) A1 clicks on Sync All\r\n\r\nExpected:\r\nA2 is a mutual contact of B1\r\n\r\n### Syncing after pairing\r\n\r\n1) A1 creates an account, enables mutual contact requests\r\n2) A2 creates an account\r\n3)  A1 & A2 enables pairing\r\n4) B1 creates an account, enables mutual contact requests\r\n5) A1 sends a contact request to B1\r\n6) B1 accepts the contact request\r\n\r\nExpected:\r\nA2 is a mutual contact of B1\r\n\r\n",
